@startuml
title RabbitMQ async work after payment webhook

actor Stripe
participant "StripeWebhookController" as Webhook
participant "CheckoutSessionService" as Checkout
database "Postgres" as DB
participant "OutboxEventScheduler" as Scheduler
participant "OutboxEventProcessor" as Processor
queue "RabbitMQ\nmovie-reservation.events" as Rabbit
participant "BookingEmailConsumer" as Email

Stripe -> Webhook: checkout.session.completed
Webhook -> Checkout: finalize payment
Checkout -> DB: update checkout/reservation\ninsert outbox_events row
DB --> Checkout: commit
Checkout --> Webhook: success
Webhook --> Stripe: 2xx

Scheduler -> Processor: processDueEvents()
Processor -> DB: claim due outbox events
Processor -> Rabbit: publish payload + headers
Rabbit -> Email: route to movie-reservation.email
Email -> Email: log would-send email
Processor -> DB: mark PUBLISHED

@enduml
